<div class="result-content">
<h3>SSC Grading System</h3>

<p>New SSC Grade Point Average (GPA) Sytem implemented from this year</p>

<p>The SSC Board has now changed the Grading system wherein the passed candidates will be alloted grades according to their marks. The Grades are given from
A1 to E, including the failure students. the changes will be implemented from this year.</p>

</div>


<div class="result-table1">

