<div class="result-table2">

<h4>Example : Suppose a student got the grades as below</h4>
<table class="below-grade-point">
<tbody>
<tr class="below-grade-point-head odd"><td>Subject</td><td>Grade</td> <td>Grade Point</td></tr>
<tr class="even"><td>Telugu</td><td>A2</td> <td>9</td></tr>
<tr class="odd"><td>Hindi</td><td>A1</td> <td>10</td></tr>
<tr class="even"><td>English</td><td>B1</td> <td>8</td></tr>
<tr class="odd"><td>Mathematics</td><td>A1</td> <td>10</td></tr>
<tr class="even"><td>Science</td><td>A1</td> <td>10</td></tr>
<tr class="odd"><td>Social Studies</td><td>A1</td><td>10</td></tr>
<tr class="even"><td colspan="4">&nbsp;</td></tr>
<tr class="below-grade-point-note odd"><td colspan="4">So, the Grade Point Average (GPA) of the student is : 9+10+8+10+10+10 = 57/6 = 9.5 Points</td></tr>
</tbody>
</table>

</div>

